          <avActivityHighlights>The wind slabs can be released easily in some places in particular on steep shady slopes. Weak layers in the old snowpack necessitate caution and restraint. &lt;br/&gt; As a consequence of warming moist small and medium sized avalanches are to be expected.</avActivityHighlights>
